Pass Pass 1S Pass 2D Pass 2H Pass 2S Pass Pass Pass
{South passes - what should you open? 
South now bids 2\D.  
Since South originally passed this is <b>NOT</b> 2/1 Game Force. Instead, it is non-forcing and shows 11 or more points. 
You should show your 4-card \H suit. South gives a preference to 2\S.  What do you do now? 

Knowing that South does not have opening strength you pass 2\S.}

